===Etymology===
From Slavic *''svaba'', compare ''[[svoboda]]''.

===Adjective===
'''vapaa''' ('''vapaampi''', '''vapain''')

# [[Free]], not imprisoned or enslaved.
#:''vapaa mies'' (free man)
# Not filled with activity or work, [[spare]].
#:''vapaa-aika'' (free time)
# Not taken by anybody, [[vacant]].
#:''Istuin on vapaa.'' (The seat is vacant.)
# Not married, [[single]].

===Noun===
'''vapaa'''

# [[leave]] (from work, etc.)

